        public static <T extends org.openqa.selenium.SearchContext> java.util.function.Predicate<T> shouldContainElements​(MultipleSearchSupplier<?> howToFind)
        The checking of an element/widget by presence of nested elements.
        Type Parameters:
        T - is a type of element/widget
        Parameters:

      • shouldContainElements

        The checking of an element/widget by presence of nested elements
        Type Parameters:
        T - is a type of element/widget
        Parameters:
        howToFind - is the way to find nested elements.

        NOTE!!!

        When there is a timeout passed through MultipleSearchSupplier.timeOut(Duration) of the given howToFind then it is ignored here.

        Returns:
        predicate that checks/filters an element/widget
